Class TransitRouteSupplier

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.routing.TransitRouteSupplier

  • public class TransitRouteSupplier
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains structured information about a source data supplier. This additional information about data supplier has to be exposed in the client application
